              <input type="text" class="form-control mb-0" id="wallet_address" name="wallet_address" placeholder="0x4Ea07591d542d702b78CE3851b9773AC14E14b09" value="" required="">
              <p class="small">Copy the Gallery Wallet Address above.  Then go to Coinbase and paste the Gallery Wallet Address into a send ETH payment form and complete the transaction for the LOOK amount. Return to this page and click Payment Sent. 
