              <input type="text" class="form-control mb-0" id="wallet_address" name="wallet_address" placeholder="0x0d1FaE9Ae65d22355b2Ef1246F3c4778082742aF" value="" required="">
              <p class="small">To complete reservation of this artwork, payment must be sent to Look Lateral. 1. Copy the Look Lateral Wallet Address above.  2. Go to Metamask and paste the Look Lateral Wallet Address into the SEND TRANSACTION form for the = LOOK amount; click NEXT and complete the transaction. 3. Return to this page after payment is confirmed.</p> 
            </div>
        </row>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">Cancel</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary payment" data-dismiss="modal">Reserve</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
